Author: luplum
Text: Yikes....  Well, let's hope she just wasn't thinking, was nervous or just trying to be funny and instantly cringing inside. I can say stupid things sometimes when I'm not thinking and regret it at once.  If it continues... that just really sucks. Maybe there's a way you could communicate it to her that it makes you uncomfortable, without admitting your own ED (unless you're comfortable to do so)?
